OL,3,CThree people killed in two separate
OL,4,Cincidents across Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThree people have died in two separate
OL,7,Fcrashes in Northern Ireland on
OL,8,FSaturday.
OL,10,FA motorcyclist and a car driver died
OL,11,Fin in a road collision in the Glenavy
OL,12,FRoad area of Upper Ballinderry.
OL,14,FIn a separate incident one person died
OL,15,Fafter a single-vehicle crash in County
OL,16,FTyrone on Saturday night.
OL,18,FOne person has been arrested following
OL,19,Fthe crash in the Caledon area.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
