OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777302667
OL,3,CThree people killed in two separate
OL,4,Cincidents across Northern Ireland
OL,6,FPolice recieved a report of a crash on
OL,7,FSaturday of a collision in the Glenavy
OL,8,FRoad area of Upper Ballinderry shortly
OL,9,Fbefore 6pm.
OL,11,FWhile emergency services attended the
OL,12,Fscene, the drivers of both vehicles
OL,13,Fwere pronounced deceased at the scene.
OL,15,FAnother person was taken to hospital
OL,16,Ffor treatment to their injuries.
OL,18,FSinn Fein councillor in Lisburn,
OL,19,FDeclan Lynch, said he is "devastated
OL,20,Fto hear this tragic news"
OL,26,@{D@ZOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
