OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777302667
OL,3,CThree people killed in two separate
OL,4,Cincidents across Northern Ireland
OL,6,F"My thoughts are with the families and
OL,7,Ffriends of the two people, who will be
OL,8,Fleft heartbroken and in shock," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"I want to commend the emergency
OL,12,Fservices for their work at the scene
OL,13,Fand would urge anyone with information
OL,14,For footage to come forward to the
OL,15,Fpolice."
OL,17,FAt 11pm police recieved another report
OL,18,Fof a crash on the Derrycourtney Road
OL,19,Fin Co Tyrone involving a van.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@_O]sD@AOUwD@HO]
