OL,3,CThree people killed in two separate
OL,4,Cincidents across Northern Ireland
OL,6,FAs officers attended the crash one
OL,7,Fperson was pronounced deceased at the
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,FOne arrest has been made and our
OL,11,Fenquiries are continuing.
OL,13,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,14,For dash-cam footage for both incidents.
